welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Green Cove Springs, a charming city known for its natural beauty and historic landmarks. We're excited for you to experience all that our city has to offer and hope you enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Jacksonville NAS Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Jacksonville NAS Airport is used for military personnel and their families.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at St Augustine Airport houses all the necessary facilities for travelers, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at St Augustine Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering amenities such as a lounge and concierge services.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.
